      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们想做一个关于基础设施即代码成功因素的饼图，标题就叫「Success with Infrastructure as Code」。核心是想说明技术能力其实只占一部分，组织变革这些软性因素同样关键。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pie",
        "title",
        "Technical Excellence",
        "Organisational Change"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，那四个板块的比例您有想法吗？我初步理解是技术卓越占大头，组织变革次之，剩下安全和持续改进再分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Technical Excellence",
        "Organisational Change",
        "Security & Compliance",
        "Continuous Improvement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，技术卓越给35%，组织变革30%，安全和合规20%，持续改进15%。这样加起来100%，也能体现我们常说的「工具易买，文化难改」。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Technical Excellence",
        "Organisational Change",
        "Security & Compliance",
        "Continuous Improvement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把这四个板块按您说的比例画出来。技术卓越35%，组织变革30%，安全合规20%，持续改进15%。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Technical Excellence",
        "Organisational Change",
        "Security & Compliance",
        "Continuous Improvement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "看起来比例是对的，不过「Organisational Change」这个词在图例里显示有点长，会不会影响可读性？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Organisational Change"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
